<section
    class="min-h-screen flex flex-col items-center justify-center relative py-32 bg-[#022c22] text-green-500 font-mono overflow-hidden"
>
    
    <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-10 overflow-hidden pointer-events-none">
        <div class="data-stream" style="left: 10%">101010101010</div>
        <div class="data-stream" style="left: 30%; animation-delay: 1s">001100110011</div>
        <div class="data-stream" style="left: 50%; animation-delay: 2s">111000111000</div>
        <div class="data-stream" style="left: 70%; animation-delay: 0.5s">010101010101</div>
        <div class="data-stream" style="left: 90%; animation-delay: 1.5s">100010001000</div>
    </div>

    <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-4xl text-center relative z-10">
        <div class="mb-16">
            <span class="text-green-700 font-mono text-xs tracking-widest uppercase mb-4 block"
                >2019</span
            >
            <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold mb-8 text-green-400">Adiós a la Materia</h2>
            <p class="text-lg text-green-800/80 leading-relaxed">
                Jubilamos al "Gran K". Ya no confiamos en objetos que pueden ensuciarse o perder
                átomos.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div
            class="bg-black border border-green-500/30 p-10 rounded-lg shadow-[0_0_50px_rgba(0,255,0,0.1)] inline-block"
        >
            <p class="text-sm text-green-600 mb-4 font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">
                La Nueva Definición
            </p>
            <code class="text-2xl md:text-4xl text-green-400 block mb-6 font-bold">
                h = 6.62607015 × 10⁻³⁴
            </code>
            <p class="text-sm text-green-800 max-w-md mx-auto">
                Ahora el kilogramo se define fijando el valor numérico de la <strong
                    >Constante de Planck</strong
                >. Hemos atado nuestras medidas a las leyes fundamentales e inmutables del universo.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    .data-stream {
        position: absolute;
        top: -100%;
        font-size: 20px;
        writing-mode: vertical-rl;
        text-orientation: upright;
        animation: fall 5s linear infinite;
        white-space: nowrap;
        color: #0f0;
        text-shadow: 0 0 5px #0f0;
    }

    @keyframes fall {
        to {
            transform: translateY(200vh);
        }
    }
</style>
